          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": " NOTES"
        }
      ]
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "content",
    "lines": [
      [
        {
          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": "The use of these hook functions is not safe in multithreaded programs,"
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": "and they are now deprecated."
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": "From glibc 2.24 onwards, the"
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "MACRO_INLINE",
          "content": ".B",
          "translatable": false
        },
        {
          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": " __malloc_initialize_hook"
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": "variable has been removed from the API."
        }
      ]
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "comment",
    "lines": [
      [
        {
          "type": "COMMENT_BLOCK",
          "content": ".\\\" https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=450187"
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "COMMENT_BLOCK",
          "content": ".\\\" http://sourceware.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=9957"
        }
      ]
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "content",
    "lines": [
      [
        {
          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": "Programmers should instead preempt calls to the relevant functions"
        }
      ],
      [
        {
          "type": "TEXT",
          "content": "by defining and exporting functions such as \"malloc\" and \"free\"."
        }
